OL,3,CLarge fire at recycling plant in Derry
OL,5,FA fire has broken out in 700 tonnes of
OL,6,Fscrap metal at an industrial estate in
OL,7,FLondonderry.
OL,9,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,10,Fat the Campsie Industrial Estate,
OL,11,FClooney Road, Derry.
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Fire & Rescue Service
OL,14,F(NIFRS) Spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"NIFRS received at a call to a
OL,17,Frecycling site at Clooney Road,
OL,18,FLondonderry at 2:58pm.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
