OL,3,CLarge fire at recycling plant in Derry
OL,5,F"Six fire appliances are now in
OL,6,Fattendance from Crescent Link,
OL,7,FLimavady, Coleraine, Ballymoney and
OL,8,FMaghera Fire Stations, with Water
OL,9,FTenders from Dungiven and Pomeroy Fire
OL,10,FStations, and a Command Support Unit
OL,11,Ffrom Strabane Fire Station.
OL,13,F"The fire is in approximately 700 to
OL,14,F800 tonnes of scrap metal.
OL,16,F"51 firefighters are currently working
OL,17,Fto bring the fire under control and
OL,18,Fprevent escalation.
